<br>
We are now on the same hitpoint table as skalds, a tank class. There is no way that Mythic will raise us higher than that.<br>
<br>
This makes the HP problem one of Con. Personally I think the +3 Dex, +2 Qui, +1 Str every 3 levels needs to be changed for SBs to +2 Str, +2 Dex, +1 Qui, +1 Con, but this wont happen because no class gets points over 4 stats, despite it still being 6 points every 3 levels.<br>
<br>
