<br>
Dex +3, Str +2, Con +1.<br>
<br>
(Hmm, + Dex, how totally unuseful to a 2H CritBlade, &quot;you evede&quot;, &quot;you ignore the evade style as you wont hit in time anyway&quot;).<br>
<br>
:-)<br>
